calls.summary: Maria wants to start healthy meal delivery for families in Austin
calls.transcript: Hi Sarah, my name is Maria Lopez and my email is maria@healthyeats.com. I want to start a healthy meal delivery business because I am passionate about helping busy parents feed their families nutritious food. The problem is that most meal delivery services focus on convenience over health. I want to create something different - a service that delivers fresh, organic, family-sized meals that kids will actually eat. My target customers are working parents who care about nutrition but dont have time to meal plan and shop. I think I can make $50,000 per month serving families in Austin, Texas. I need about $75,000 to start with the commercial kitchen and initial marketing.
